ing: 4 teaspoons canned chipotle chile peppers in adobo sauce, finely chopped
des: "Beans pack more protein than any other plant food, plus fiber, zinc, potassium, magnesium, calcium and iron -- with plenty of antioxidants and little fat. Warning: This baked bean recipe isn't for the timid."
ins: Preheat oven to 350 degrees. In a large bowl combine all ingredients. Spray a 7x11 shallow baking dish. Add bean mixture. Bake 45 minutes.
